</p></list-item></list>All the participants were sitting in front of a 17&#x000a0;in. computer screen, at a distance of 50&#x000a0;cm approximately as illustrated in Fig.&#x000a0;<xref rid="Fig3" ref-type="fig">3</xref>. The screen resolution was 136&#x000a0;&#x000d7;&#x000a0;768 pixels. The whole session lasted about 25&#x02013;30 min.</p></sec><sec id="Sec12"><title>Statistical analysis</title><p id="Par41">The mean and standard deviation were used for the description of clinical scale scores. The percentage improvement was evaluated as<disp-formula id="Equ3"><label>3</label><alternatives><tex-math id="M7">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
